4) Create a new class UnaryOperators and add a main method

New email notification. Your received one more email:
-declare int inbox with value 10
-increase inbox by 1 and print out inbox count

During the gaming, one life is lost:
-declare int lives with value 3
-decrease lives by 1 and print out Lives left

Show a negative temperature reading:
-declare int temperature with value 15.
-use - to change it to negative and assign to belowZero variable.
-print the result.
